<h2>Showcase</h2>
<p class="explanation">
  This project is a group of small independent modules made to showcare various gameplay mechanisms made under Unity<br/>
  They all are various state of progress, improving them when I see fit, feel free to use the buttons below to try them!
  Most of these projects are still heavily work in progress but I'm planning to improve them bit by bit
</p>
<p id="unity-loading">
  Loading...
</p>
<div id="unity-container" class="unity-desktop">
  <canvas id="unity-canvas" width=960 height=600 tabindex="-1"></canvas>
  <div id="unity-warning"></div>
</div>
<div id="unity-buttons">
  {% for s in sketch %}
  <button class="button" id="sketch-{{ s.id }}" data-scene="{{ s.scene }}">{{ s.name }}</button>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
<div id="unity-explanations">
  <fieldset>
    <legend>Explanations</legend>
    {% for s in sketch %}
    <div id="sketch-{{ s.id }}-expl" hidden>
    {{ s.explanations | join("<br>") | raw }}
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </fieldset>
</div>